#/-------------------[DOTENV_PUBLIC_KEY]--------------------/
#/            public-key encryption for .env files          /
#/       [how it works](https://dotenvx.com/encryption)     /
#/----------------------------------------------------------/
DOTENV_PUBLIC_KEY="this_will_be_auto_generated"

- `GEMINI_API_KEY` is required for the local dev middleware that proxies requests to the Gemini API.
- `REPOVIEW_DEV_TOKEN` is required for the local dev middleware that proxies requests to the RepoView API.
- `GITHUB_TOKEN` is required for the local dev middleware that proxies requests to the GitHub API.

GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here
REPOVIEW_DEV_TOKEN=your_repoview_dev_token_here
GITHUB_TOKEN=your_github_token_here
ALLOW_EXTERNAL_WRITES=true # optional
EXTERNAL_WRITE_SECRET="your_special_secret_key_here"